title: Photos: Dan Campbell's first practice as Dolphins coach
text:
Photos: Dan Campbell's first practice as Dolphins coach Caption CAMPBELL Joe Cavaretta / Sun Sentinel Miami Dolphins new interim coach Dan Campbell speaks with the media, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, at the training facility at Nova Southeastern University in Davie. JOE CAVARETTA/STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER Miami Dolphins new interim coach Dan Campbell speaks with the media, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, at the training facility at Nova Southeastern University in Davie. JOE CAVARETTA/STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER (Joe Cavaretta / Sun Sentinel) Caption Coyle Joe Cavaretta / Sun Sentinel Miami Dolphins defensive coordinator Kevin Coyle is seen during practice, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, at the training facility at Nova Southeastern University in Davie. JOE CAVARETTA/STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER Miami Dolphins defensive coordinator Kevin Coyle is seen during practice, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, at the training facility at Nova Southeastern University in Davie. JOE CAVARETTA/STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER (Joe Cavaretta / Sun Sentinel) 
Dan Campbell's physical and aggressive style was on display at Wednesday's practice. Joe Cavaretta
